@startuml
title UC05: Game lifecycle states

[*] --> WaitingUsers
WaitingUsers --> Ready : users >= 2
Ready --> RunningBattles : admin start battles
RunningBattles --> Paused : admin pause battles
Paused --> RunningBattles : admin start battles
RunningBattles --> Finished : admin finish game\nor winner resolved
Finished --> WaitingUsers : admin reset game
WaitingUsers --> WaitingUsers : admin new user
WaitingUsers --> [*] : admin clear users

@enduml

